The current Chart API only allow setting of very limited data as tooltip or label to the pie chart which does not include include information about what each slice is representing (like that of the legend).


// tooltip trigger
Action tooltipAction = ActionImpl.create(ActionType.SHOW_TOOLTIP_LITERAL, TooltipValueImpl.create(500, null));
Trigger tooltipTrigger = TriggerImpl.create(TriggerCondition.ONMOUSEOVER_LITERAL, tooltipAction);
